DLTB = Download tamilbeat
       ^   ^    ^    ^


Introduction:
Given an URL as a input, dltb downloads all the mp3 
files! 


USAGE:
./dltb <tamilbeat.com URL>


EXAMPLE:
./dltb http://www.tamilat.com/tamilsongs


